Rory McIlroy is hoping to complete the career grand slam of majors at the Masters . 
  The world number one is looking to become the sixth player to win all four major titles . 
  He has revealed his final-round collapse at Augusta National in 2011 was the most important day of his career . 
  The 25-year-old believes it is 'unthinkable' he will not win the Masters this year . 
 